        <ul>
            <li>Unauthorized access to student information systems</li>
            <li>Potential for serious harm including academic identity theft</li>
            <li>Requirement to report breaches involving student data</li>
            <li>Special sensitivity of minors' information in breaches</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Student-Specific Privacy Concerns</h2>
